data.description: MOVE IN READY! Discover the epitome of traditional charm in this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse nestled in the heart of Greer, SC. This home seamlessly combines classic design with modern conveniences, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step into a spacious and inviting interior with an open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Experience a sense of openness and flow that complements your lifestyle. The heart of this home is its kitchen, featuring brand-new appliances that add a touch of modernity to your culinary experience. Cooking becomes a joy in this well-equipped and stylish space. Enjoy privacy and outdoor living in your fenced backyard. Seller is offering a 14-month home guarantee, providing peace of mind for you as you settle into your new home. This commitment reflects the confidence in the quality and condition of the property.
